{"type":"message","id":"24159c5a","parentId":"2afe9728","timestamp":"2026-05-20T18:13:51.902Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"关键问题确认：\n1. WebSocket 连接正常 ✅\n2. Device count: 1 ✅（有设备）\n3. WASM container 有内容（19974 chars）✅\n4. connectedDevice: None ❌（未设置）\n5. g_bLoggedIn2: False ❌（未登录）\n6. g_bPlaying2: False ❌\n7. 点击连接按钮后，connectedDevice仍然是None ❌\n\n这说明问题：\n- connectDevice 函数被调用，但没有正确设置 window.connectedDevice\n- WASM SDK 的 clickLogin2 未被调用，或调用后失败\n\n需要检查截图，然后分析问题根因。\n\n根据之前看到的 base.html 代码：\n1. IIFE 内部的 connectedDevice 是局部变量\n2. 全局 script 块里的 connectedDevice = null 在 DOMContentLoaded 前执行\n3. IIFE 内部的 connectDevice 函数设置的是 window.connectedDevice（IIFE内）\n4. 但全局 script 块的 connectedDevice 没有被更新\n\n问题：两个 connectedDevice 变量存在冲突。\n\n让我看截图来确认视觉状态。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**关键发现**：\n- `connectedDevice: None` - 连接按钮未更新全局状态\n- `g_bLoggedIn2: False` - WASM SDK 未登录\n\n看截图分析问题："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_tool-79f4ea1c9c904db4b5942c9112172360","name":"image","arguments":{"image":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/screenshots/01_main_021326.png","prompt":"分析这个仪表盘页面：显示什么内容？WebSocket状态是什么？设备数量？是否有在线设备？"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_tool-56815774600a4f9289678592265243cc","name":"image","arguments":{"image":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/screenshots/03_console_*.png","prompt":"分析主控台页面：WASM播放器区域显示什么？是否灰色/空白？是否显示视频？"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"YerPlan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":330,"output":394,"cacheRead":58240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58964,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779300818217,"responseId":"msg_4ab61ea2-1bb6-4e2e-9c8c-70051db154da"}}
