{"type":"message","id":"d06131dd","parentId":"b5a5d38c","timestamp":"2026-05-20T18:14:20.147Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题清晰了：\n1. IIFE 内部：`var connectedDevice = null;` - 局部变量\n2. 全局 script块：`var connectedDevice = null;` - 另一个独立的全局变量\n3. WASM SDK 的 `clickLogin2()` 检查 `window.connectedDevice`\n4. 但 IIFE 内的代码如 `connectDevice` 函数用的是局部变量 `connectedDevice`，而非 `window.connectedDevice`\n\n虽然 IIFE 内某些地方写了 `connectedDevice = window.connectedDevice = {...}`，但大多数地方只写 `connectedDevice = {...}`，只更新局部变量。\n\n修复方案：\n1. **删除全局 script 块中的 `var connectedDevice = null;`**\n2. **IIFE 内部删除 `var connectedDevice = null;`，改为从 window 读取**\n3. **所有赋值操作改为 `window.connectedDevice = ...`**\n4. **所有读取改为 `window.connectedDevice`**\n\n但这需要大量修改。更简单的方法：\n- 保留 IIFE 内的 `connectedDevice` 局部变量用于内部逻辑\n- 但在需要 WASM SDK 交互时，同步到 `window.connectedDevice`\n\n看代码中已经有 `connectedDevice = window.connectedDevice = {...}` 的模式，说明之前已经尝试同步。\n\n问题是：connectDevice 函数在某些分支只更新了局部变量。\n\n让我检查 connectDevice 函数的完整逻辑...\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"问题已清晰：`connectedDevice` 是局部变量，WASM SDK 检查的是 `window.connectedDevice`。\n\n检查关键更新点，确保所有地方都同步到 `window.connectedDevice`："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_tool-a1c1dcc1fc05409fa1e985677ef5f19f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content \"D:\\astro_py\\astro_hub\\src\\web\\base.html\" | Select-String \"connectedDevice\\s*=\" -Context 0,2 | Select-Object -First 20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"YerPlan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3398,"output":393,"cacheRead":59136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62927,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779300848950,"responseId":"msg_88f7632a-1aa8-4980-8d36-b5d4015a49a3"}}
